These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, hiking, card-games, collecting
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, adventure, thriller, horror
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, surfing, golf, tennis
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, boat, roller, bus
 1. the person who's sport is surfing is not to the right of the person who's sport is parkour##8
 2. the person driving the snowmobile is not to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##8
 3. the person driving the bus is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is parkour is not to the left of the person who's sport is tennis##8
 5. the person driving the snowmobile is not to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##8
 6. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 7. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##5
 8. the person watching horror movies is between the person driving the boat and the person who's sport is surfing##2
 9. the person driving the bus is the person watching thriller movies##1
10. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
11. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
12. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
13. the person watching thriller movies is not to the left of the person driving the bus##8
14. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person driving the roller##1
15. the person who's hobby is hiking is not the person who's sport is surfing##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | photography     | hiking   | collecting | card-games |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | horror   | action   | thriller  |
| Sport         | surfing  | golf  | tennis  | parkour |
| Transport     | snowmobile    | roller | boat     | bus    |

