.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, soy-milk, coffee, fanta
There 4 different types of food: lemon, tomato, pineapple, watermelon
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, metal, classical, r&b
4 different pets are kept: mouse, horse, lizard, snake
 1. the fan of classical is between the owner of the mouse and the fan of metal##2
 2. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the right of the owner of the horse##8
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person eating lemon##3
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is not to the right of the owner of the snake##8
 5. the owner of the mouse is not to the left of the fan of metal##8
 6. the person eating watermelon is not to the right of the person drinking fanta##8
 7. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the owner of the snake##5
 8. the owner of the lizard is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of rock is the owner of the horse##1
10. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
11. the owner of the mouse is not to the left of the fan of classical##8
12. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
13. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the right of the person eating tomato##5
14. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
15. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
17. the person drinking almond-milk is not to the right of the fan of metal##8
18. the person eating tomato is not to the right of the owner of the horse##8
19. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person eating tomato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | coffee | fanta  | soy-milk  |
| Food          | watermelon     | tomato | lemon | pineapple  |
| Music-Genre   | metal    | classical  | r&b | rock |
| Pet           | lizard | snake | mouse    | horse  |

