.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, fishing, chess, writing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, horror, disaster, adventure
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, indie, techno, d&b
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, soccer, swimming, skateboarding
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 2. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is chess##5
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the left of the person watching adventure movies##5
 4. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the right of the fan of trance##5
 5. the person who's sport is swimming is not to the right of the person watching spy movies##8
 6. the person who's hobby is writing is not to the left of the person watching disaster movies##8
 7. the fan of techno is in an odd position##4
 8. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
 9. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
10. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far right##1
11. the person watching spy movies is not to the left of the fan of indie##8
12. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | photography    | writing   | chess | fishing |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | disaster  | adventure   | horror      |
| Music-Genre   | indie | trance    | techno      | d&b       |
| Sport         | swimming    | ice-hockey | skateboarding   | soccer    |

