.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-4::.
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, grapefruit, pear, lemon
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, filmmaking, sudoku, writing
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, bartender, paramedic, coach
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, cricket, cycling, baseball
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not the lawyer##6
 2. the coach is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
 3. the person eating lemon is the paramedic##1
 4. the person eating grapefruit is between the lawyer and the bartender##2
 5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
 6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not to the right of the person eating grapefruit##8
 7. the person who's hobby is writing is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5
 9. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the coach##1
10. the bartender is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
11. the person who's sport is cricket is not to the right of the person eating strawberry##8
12. the lawyer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
13. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
14. the bartender is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
15. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |         2          |    3    |    4     |
| Food    | pear    | grapefruit             | strawberry   | lemon     |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | sudoku            | writing | filmmaking    |
| Job     | bartender | coach | lawyer  | paramedic |
| Sport   | snowboarding  | cricket               | cycling  | baseball   |

