There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, american, canadian, brazilian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, baseball, swimming, sailing
 1. the person watching musical movies is not to the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##8
 2. the brazilian is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 3. the person who's sport is baseball is not the person who's hobby is hiking##6
 4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 5. the person watching musical movies is not to the right of the canadian##8
 6. the person who's sport is swimming is not to the right of the person watching musical movies##8
 7. the person who's sport is baseball is not to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##8
 8. the american is the person watching action movies##1
 9. the indonesian is not to the left of the person who's hobby is baking##8
10. the person watching fantasy movies is not to the left of the person watching musical movies##8
11. the person who's sport is sailing is between the person who's hobby is baking and the person watching action movies##2
12. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
13. the american is not to the right of the person watching action movies##8
14. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
