.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, coffee, milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, coach, dressmaker, fisherman
There are 4 different nationalities: french, malaysian, indian, egyptian
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, taxi, roller, motorbike
 1. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
 2. the person driving the car is not to the left of the fisherman##8
 3. the person driving the car is not to the left of the person drinking milk##8
 4. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5
 5. the person driving the roller is the indian##1
 6. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the malaysian##8
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not the egyptian##6
 8. the coach is somewhere between the person driving the roller and the person drinking hot-chocolate##7
 9. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the right of the coach##5
10. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the coach##3
11. the dressmaker is on the right of the project-manager##1
12. the coach is not the french##6
13. the malaysian is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
14. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
15. the person driving the car is not to the right of the coach##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate    | milk   | coffee        | cola  |
| Job           | fisherman     | coach | project-manager | dressmaker  |
| Nationality   | french | egyptian    | indian   | malaysian     |
| Transport     | motorbike       | car     | roller    | taxi |

