.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, fanta, soy-milk, sprite
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, baking, puzzles, fishing
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, musician, scientist, engineer
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, skateboard, van, subway
 1. the musician is on the left or right of the engineer##3
 2. the person driving the ship is not the person who's hobby is filmmaking##6
 3. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##5
 4. the scientist is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is in an even position##4
 6. the person driving the subway is somewhere between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking fanta##7
 7. the person driving the subway is not to the left of the person driving the van##8
 8. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is baking##7
 9. the security-guard is on the far left or far right##3
10. the musician is not to the left of the musician##8
11. the security-guard is on the far left##1
12. the engineer is on the far right##1
13. the person driving the subway is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
14. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not to the left of the person drinking fanta##8
15. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
16. the musician is not to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4       |
| Beverage    | fanta        | hot-chocolate      | sprite      | soy-milk          |
| Hobby       | fishing | puzzles     | filmmaking | baking       |
| Job         | security-guard | scientist | musician  | engineer |
| Transport   | van        | subway         | skateboard        | ship     |

