 7. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the fan of techno##1
 8. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the owner of the lizard##5
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is not the owner of the frog##6
10. the owner of the lizard is in an even position##4
11. the person drinking tea is not to the left of the person driving the tram##8
12. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
13. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
14. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

