The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, train, car, taxi
 1. the person drinking fanta is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 2. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 3. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person driving the taxi##5
 4. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
 6. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
 7. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
 8. the person driving the train is not to the right of the person who's sport is handball##8
 9. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
10. the person drinking sprite is not to the right of the fan of dubstep##8
11. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
12. the person driving the taxi is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of hip-hop is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is handball##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | cola   | 7up     | fanta    | sprite |
| Music-Genre   | gospel  | jazz      | hip-hop     | dubstep     |
| Sport         | volleyball | rowing  | parkour     | handball  |
| Transport     | helicopter     | car | taxi | train     |

